1
00:00:12,750 --> 00:00:14,210
Here's the plan for today.

2
00:00:14,480 --> 00:00:16,680
All members of the investigation team,

3
00:00:16,760 --> 00:00:17,620
except Li Qian,

4
00:00:17,920 --> 00:00:20,320
will participate in tonight's operation.

5
00:00:20,550 --> 00:00:22,320
The core members involved in the arrest

6
00:00:22,320 --> 00:00:23,320
will all be armed.

7
00:00:25,100 --> 00:00:26,280
To prevent Mei Dong

8
00:00:26,370 --> 00:00:28,510
from sending someone
to stake out near our station,

9
00:00:28,510 --> 00:00:29,440
we will all

10
00:00:29,980 --> 00:00:31,070
act as usual

11
00:00:31,220 --> 00:00:32,350
[Police]

12
00:00:31,620 --> 00:00:33,390
and get off work in plain clothes.

13
00:00:33,390 --> 00:00:34,280
Once outside,

14
00:00:34,320 --> 00:00:37,450
we will gather at
our respective designated locations.

15
00:00:38,220 --> 00:00:40,030
With Guanlan Hotel as the center,

16
00:00:40,030 --> 00:00:41,960
we will set up surveillance
in all key areas

17
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:44,210
within a one-kilometer radius.

18
00:00:44,320 --> 00:00:46,870
This will form a comprehensive

19
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:49,460
and mutually supporting encirclement.

20
00:00:50,380 --> 00:00:51,970
Also, all the hotel's entrances and exits

21
00:00:51,970 --> 00:00:54,150
must be staked out
by experienced officers.

22
00:00:54,150 --> 00:00:54,770
Song Xing,

23
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:56,210
you are in charge of
keeping an eye on Yang Wei.

24
00:00:56,210 --> 00:00:57,810
After Yang Wei meets with the contact,

25
00:00:57,810 --> 00:01:00,030
if it is confirmed to be Mei Dong,

26
00:01:00,170 --> 00:01:01,590
release the information as planned.

27
00:01:01,590 --> 00:01:03,320
You will lead the team to make the arrest.

28
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,069
If the person who shows up

29
00:01:04,069 --> 00:01:05,840
is just a lackey scouting for Mei Dong,

30
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:06,770
then stand down.

31
00:01:07,150 --> 00:01:07,880
Understood?

32
00:01:08,070 --> 00:01:09,670
-Understood!
-Understood!

33
00:01:10,980 --> 00:01:11,710
Understood.

34
00:01:19,350 --> 00:01:19,760
Chief Zhang,

35
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:21,220
is this arrangement okay?

36
00:01:22,710 --> 00:01:23,310
Smooth

37
00:01:24,039 --> 00:01:24,980
and detailed.

38
00:01:25,430 --> 00:01:26,630
Okay, I'll go watch the monitors.

39
00:01:26,630 --> 00:01:27,340
I'll go too.

40
00:01:28,789 --> 00:01:29,650
You rest.

41
00:01:29,670 --> 00:01:31,560
I'll carefully handle the whole thing.

42
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:32,590
Detailed.

43
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:36,240
Isn't it the same?

44
00:03:01,940 --> 00:03:05,660
[Born with Luck]

45
00:03:05,690 --> 00:03:08,620
[Episode 14]

46
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:42,190
[September 7, 2012]

47
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:43,350
Go.

48
00:03:43,390 --> 00:03:44,600
Reassure him.

49
00:03:52,030 --> 00:03:53,490
Sir, what would you like to drink?

50
00:03:53,490 --> 00:03:54,020
Nothing.

51
00:03:55,590 --> 00:03:56,910
Act like a man.

52
00:03:56,930 --> 00:03:58,560
Our guys are all around here.

53
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,270
Yang Wei?

54
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:30,970
The room is booked.

55
00:04:30,970 --> 00:04:31,800
Let's go up.

56
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:48,560
Did you come back with Dong

57
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,760
from Southeast Asia?

58
00:04:55,510 --> 00:04:56,970
Are you guys usually busy?

59
00:05:03,660 --> 00:05:04,620
Is he doing well?

60
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,540
Let's go, Yang.

61
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:23,510
Dong.

62
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:26,430
Dong.

63
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,120
Phone.

64
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:32,800
What?

65
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,360
It's the rule.

66
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,000
Yang,

67
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:37,510
we're responsible for Dong's safety.

68
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:38,680
If anything goes wrong,

69
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,480
we'd be too ashamed
to stay in the business.

70
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,740
You are Dong's friend,

71
00:05:41,870 --> 00:05:43,130
so please understand.

72
00:05:44,190 --> 00:05:45,000
We're doing this

73
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,130
for Dong's own good.

74
00:05:46,750 --> 00:05:49,550
Don't make things difficult
for us subordinates.

75
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:01,240
Password.

76
00:06:17,750 --> 00:06:18,680
Leave it with me.

77
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,720
What are you doing?

78
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,260
Yang.

79
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:28,120
Yang,

80
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,290
bear with us.

81
00:06:54,310 --> 00:06:54,970
Come, Yang,

82
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:56,250
sit down. Come.

83
00:06:58,159 --> 00:06:59,890
Your technique is pretty good.

84
00:07:06,310 --> 00:07:07,110
Where is Dong?

85
00:07:08,750 --> 00:07:09,310
Yang,

86
00:07:09,950 --> 00:07:11,750
Dong tried to contact Lin Kai,

87
00:07:12,950 --> 00:07:14,550
but his phone was turned off.

88
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,520
Later, he called his home,

89
00:07:16,950 --> 00:07:18,750
and his wife said Lin Kai is dead.

90
00:07:19,510 --> 00:07:20,840
Did you know about this?

91
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:26,390
How did Lin Kai die?

92
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:27,800
I don't know.

93
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:29,720
The police

94
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,380
are investigating it, right?

95
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:32,560
And they refuse to

96
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,820
disclose any details.

97
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,070
All I know is that Kai's body

98
00:07:37,070 --> 00:07:38,480
was found in an empty lot.

99
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,520
From what you're saying,

100
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,260
did the police come to you?

101
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,000
When he had the accident,

102
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,280
he was driving my car.

103
00:07:47,930 --> 00:07:49,659
I shouldn't have lent it to him.

104
00:07:50,130 --> 00:07:52,730
As soon as I lent it to him,
something happened.

105
00:07:54,409 --> 00:07:55,320
Did the police

106
00:07:55,390 --> 00:07:56,990
ask you about anything else,

107
00:07:57,110 --> 00:07:58,060
such as about business?

108
00:07:58,060 --> 00:07:59,390
How could they not ask?

109
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,080
I just kept my mouth shut.

110
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,240
Since they don't have

111
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,000
anything on me,

112
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,330
what could they do to me?

113
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,800
When the time was up, they just let me go.

114
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:20,720
Hello?

115
00:08:21,190 --> 00:08:22,240
Sir, do you want a massage?

116
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:22,680
No.

117
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,240
Sir, the spa is on the third floor.

118
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,480
You can come over and try it,

119
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,410
or we can come up.

120
00:08:27,510 --> 00:08:27,970
No need.

121
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:28,760
Thank you.

122
00:08:44,870 --> 00:08:45,520
Hello?

123
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:54,750
Okay.

124
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:58,880
Yang,

125
00:08:59,440 --> 00:08:59,970
let's go.

126
00:09:01,550 --> 00:09:02,480
Where is Dong?

127
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:15,850
Let's go.

128
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:30,900
Aren't there elevators here?

129
00:09:34,890 --> 00:09:38,650
[Guest room corridor 4]

130
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:22,340
Yang,

131
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:23,040
go in.

132
00:10:32,670 --> 00:10:33,600
Freeze!

133
00:10:35,390 --> 00:10:36,270
Wei.

134
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:43,970
Don't recognize me?

135
00:10:44,910 --> 00:10:45,930
D-Dong?

136
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,780
I got plastic surgery.

137
00:10:49,580 --> 00:10:51,440
Not as handsome as before, right?

138
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:52,720
What?

139
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:53,480
Sit, sit.

140
00:10:54,870 --> 00:10:55,240
Look.

141
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:58,890
Right.

142
00:11:04,050 --> 00:11:05,380
This is for your mother.

143
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,030
No, I can't.

144
00:11:11,150 --> 00:11:11,790
It's too expensive.

145
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:12,780
I can't accept this.

146
00:11:12,780 --> 00:11:13,550
We are brothers.

147
00:11:13,550 --> 00:11:15,080
Why are you being so polite?

148
00:11:16,910 --> 00:11:17,910
Is she doing well?

149
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,030
Very well.

150
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,090
That's good.

151
00:11:22,910 --> 00:11:24,530
Why are you being silly?

152
00:11:25,030 --> 00:11:26,270
My appearance has changed,

153
00:11:26,270 --> 00:11:27,580
but my voice hasn't.

154
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:28,270
Right?

155
00:11:29,030 --> 00:11:30,000
Yes, Dong.

156
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:31,960
Yes!

157
00:11:34,390 --> 00:11:36,120
Why did you suddenly come back?

158
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,330
For a business deal.

159
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:40,240
What kind of business

160
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,640
requires such a big risk?

161
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,440
A deal with Zhou Rong.

162
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,060
Think about it.

163
00:11:47,140 --> 00:11:48,690
That's too risky.

164
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:50,580
Aren't you a wanted man right now?

165
00:11:51,790 --> 00:11:53,150
How is it risky?

166
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:56,040
I used my passport

167
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:59,080
and walked openly

168
00:11:59,270 --> 00:12:00,390
through customs.

169
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,530
Dong, the phone.

170
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:24,940
Sir, do you need a massage?

171
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,900
It would be good to relax a bit.

172
00:12:49,150 --> 00:12:49,510
Dong!

173
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:11,930
[Guest room corridor 1]

174
00:13:12,030 --> 00:13:13,080
[Guest room corridor 2]

175
00:13:13,130 --> 00:13:13,470
[Guest room corridor 3]

176
00:13:13,910 --> 00:13:15,040
Yang Wei is exposed.

177
00:13:16,170 --> 00:13:19,170
Mei Dong is taking his men
to the emergency stairwell.

178
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:21,100
Mei Dong is wearing a red hoodie.

179
00:13:21,100 --> 00:13:22,360
Three people in total.

180
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:41,000
Freeze!

181
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:41,200
Police!

182
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:41,550
Freeze!

183
00:13:41,550 --> 00:13:41,960
Stop!

184
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:42,600
Police!

185
00:13:44,780 --> 00:13:45,840
-Freeze!
-Freeze!

186
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:51,680
Dong,

187
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:53,110
take care.

188
00:14:25,750 --> 00:14:27,240
Wow, resisting arrest.

189
00:14:27,260 --> 00:14:27,960
Look up.

190
00:14:33,030 --> 00:14:34,080
[Photo of Mei Dong, the suspect]

191
00:14:34,110 --> 00:14:35,420
[Wanted]

192
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:39,020
Is that him?

193
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:46,630
Captain Wang.

194
00:15:46,630 --> 00:15:47,550
What's wrong with you?

195
00:15:47,550 --> 00:15:48,080
Nothing.

196
00:15:48,150 --> 00:15:49,390
Identify him quickly.

197
00:15:49,390 --> 00:15:50,240
Look up.

198
00:15:54,270 --> 00:15:55,400
This isn't Mei Dong.

199
00:15:58,150 --> 00:15:59,150
Where is Mei Dong?

200
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:03,910
Search!

201
00:16:04,150 --> 00:16:04,510
Go.

202
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:06,320
No.

203
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:07,490
Then I...

204
00:16:12,390 --> 00:16:14,390
You are really a good friend to Dong.

205
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:15,910
Really?

206
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:42,000
Police!

207
00:17:38,540 --> 00:17:39,500
[Photo of Mei Dong, the suspect]

208
00:17:40,450 --> 00:17:41,460
[Photo of Mei Dong, the suspect]

209
00:18:40,310 --> 00:18:41,200
Attention all units.

210
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:42,310
Mei Dong has escaped.

211
00:18:42,310 --> 00:18:44,270
Keep a close eye
on all suspicious persons.

212
00:18:44,270 --> 00:18:45,160
Mei Dong had plastic surgery,

213
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:47,620
and looks different
from his wanted poster.

214
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:07,790
Be careful if you spot Mei Dong.

215
00:19:07,790 --> 00:19:08,510
He was once

216
00:19:08,510 --> 00:19:10,510
the Sanda champion of Sanjiangkou.

217
00:20:04,510 --> 00:20:05,580
Hello.

218
00:20:06,200 --> 00:20:07,000
Excuse me,

219
00:20:07,030 --> 00:20:08,000
you look quite different

220
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:08,940
from the photo.

221
00:20:09,110 --> 00:20:10,120
Are you Mei Dong?

222
00:20:10,510 --> 00:20:12,110
I dare you to let me out!

223
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:15,130
It really is him.

224
00:20:20,460 --> 00:20:28,970
♪ Snow blankets the Volga River ♪

225
00:20:27,790 --> 00:20:28,990
Attention all units.

226
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:30,710
Come to the underground loading bay.

227
00:20:30,460 --> 00:20:38,370
♪ Three cars drive over the icy river ♪

228
00:20:30,960 --> 00:20:32,310
Mei Dong has been captured.

229
00:20:32,310 --> 00:20:33,840
Mei Dong has been captured.

230
00:20:41,750 --> 00:20:43,350
This is your overseas phone.

231
00:20:43,510 --> 00:20:44,030
Right?

232
00:20:47,310 --> 00:20:48,510
You used this number

233
00:20:48,590 --> 00:20:49,640
for your MasterCard

234
00:20:49,640 --> 00:20:50,960
and Visa card.

235
00:20:51,830 --> 00:20:53,000
This is your phone.

236
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:54,160
You can't deny it.

237
00:20:58,340 --> 00:21:00,340
What kind of business are you doing?

238
00:21:04,190 --> 00:21:08,990
[Police]

239
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:11,440
This is an indictment

240
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:13,080
found on your computer.

241
00:21:12,440 --> 00:21:13,330
[Civil Complaint]

242
00:21:13,240 --> 00:21:14,200
A foreigner named

243
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:16,240
Kanokkorn Sukum is going to sue

244
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:16,960
Zhou Rong's Rongcheng locally

245
00:21:16,960 --> 00:21:19,000
for infringing the patented technology

246
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:21,160
of rapid concrete hardening

247
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:22,270
owned by Sumita Company,

248
00:21:22,270 --> 00:21:23,930
which is under her name.

249
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:26,030
The compensation is 300 million RMB.

250
00:21:26,030 --> 00:21:26,830
Rongcheng

251
00:21:26,880 --> 00:21:28,610
will lose this lawsuit, right?

252
00:21:28,790 --> 00:21:29,880
The 300 million will naturally

253
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:31,120
flow overseas

254
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:32,880
as compensation.

255
00:21:33,590 --> 00:21:36,250
You came up with
this money-laundering scheme.

256
00:21:42,310 --> 00:21:42,880
Mei Dong,

257
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,340
using this attitude

258
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:46,780
towards us is fine.

259
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:48,020
But I advise you

260
00:21:48,270 --> 00:21:49,270
not to act like this in court.

261
00:21:48,600 --> 00:21:51,040
[Before plastic surgery]

262
00:21:51,070 --> 00:21:54,130
[After plastic surgery]

263
00:21:57,590 --> 00:21:59,720
You laundered the stolen money

264
00:21:59,740 --> 00:22:02,470
from Dinghu's
illegal fundraising case, right?

265
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:05,840
There are nearly ten thousand victims.

266
00:22:06,790 --> 00:22:08,380
After losing everything,

267
00:22:08,720 --> 00:22:10,030
two jumped off buildings,

268
00:22:10,030 --> 00:22:11,490
and one laid on the tracks.

269
00:22:11,750 --> 00:22:12,880
If the families of the victims

270
00:22:12,880 --> 00:22:14,010
saw you like this...

271
00:22:16,310 --> 00:22:17,480
If you're smart,

272
00:22:17,750 --> 00:22:19,190
confess immediately

273
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:21,030
and try to get a longer sentence.

274
00:22:21,030 --> 00:22:22,070
For you,

275
00:22:22,480 --> 00:22:23,480
it's safer in jail

276
00:22:23,590 --> 00:22:24,480
than outside.

277
00:22:34,030 --> 00:22:35,360
I can't take it anymore.

278
00:22:36,510 --> 00:22:36,970
I can't.

279
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:38,960
A genuine smile

280
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:41,750
is a quarter-second micro-expression.

281
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:43,920
Anything over five seconds is fake.

282
00:22:43,960 --> 00:22:44,830
You're good.

283
00:22:45,510 --> 00:22:48,000
Aren't your facial muscles tired
after smiling for so long?

284
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:48,640
Doesn't it ache?

285
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:50,110
Or is it because of some aftereffects

286
00:22:50,110 --> 00:22:51,640
from your plastic surgery?

287
00:22:53,870 --> 00:22:54,940
[Comparison of Plastic Surgery
Before and After] [Criminal Record]

288
00:22:54,070 --> 00:22:55,400
You really went all out.

289
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:57,150
Even got it done
in the opposite direction.

290
00:22:57,150 --> 00:22:58,510
The once all-powerful leader

291
00:22:58,510 --> 00:22:59,510
of Jinshuiting

292
00:22:59,590 --> 00:23:01,440
in Sanjiangkou,

293
00:23:02,070 --> 00:23:04,270
you had no choice but to end up like this.

294
00:23:04,440 --> 00:23:05,840
Do you feel a bit wronged?

295
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:09,400
Who is Kanokkorn?

