00:35:42,670 --> 00:35:43,150
And

587
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:46,220
Mei Dong was caught by the police.

588
00:35:46,400 --> 00:35:46,760
I don't know

589
00:35:46,760 --> 00:35:48,220
what he told Zhang Yi'ang.

590
00:35:48,550 --> 00:35:49,750
Right now, the police

591
00:35:50,400 --> 00:35:51,800
might already be onto us.

592
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:52,640
So...

593
00:35:53,590 --> 00:35:54,190
watch out.

594
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:56,670
I will definitely be careful

595
00:35:56,670 --> 00:35:57,930
and keep a low profile.

596
00:35:58,320 --> 00:35:59,060
No,

597
00:35:59,150 --> 00:36:00,190
just act as usual,

598
00:36:00,230 --> 00:36:00,960
understand?

599
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:06,480
Jianren,

600
00:36:07,710 --> 00:36:09,040
I'll be honest with you.

601
00:36:09,920 --> 00:36:10,610
If East New Town's loan

602
00:36:10,610 --> 00:36:11,810
doesn't come through

603
00:36:12,440 --> 00:36:14,040
and the police target us too,

604
00:36:15,190 --> 00:36:16,250
I plan to

605
00:36:17,440 --> 00:36:18,630
leave Sanjiangkou.

606
00:36:21,320 --> 00:36:22,250
But don't worry.

607
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:24,660
I will take you with me.

608
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:27,310
Where

609
00:36:27,840 --> 00:36:28,510
would we go?

610
00:36:30,550 --> 00:36:32,550
A small island in the South Pacific,

611
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:33,710
my utopia,

612
00:36:34,230 --> 00:36:34,840
Gondwana.

613
00:36:36,030 --> 00:36:36,800
Gondwana?

614
00:36:39,550 --> 00:36:40,480
Let's eat first.

615
00:36:41,670 --> 00:36:42,800
We have to investigate,

616
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,060
but we also have to eat.

617
00:36:44,760 --> 00:36:46,820
Your brain works faster after a meal.

618
00:36:47,230 --> 00:36:47,690
Yi'ang,

619
00:36:48,480 --> 00:36:49,280
take the lead.

620
00:36:51,590 --> 00:36:52,190
Let's eat.

621
00:37:08,030 --> 00:37:09,890
Do you have any staple food there?

622
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:11,000
I was only thinking about

623
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:12,630
the dishes Chief Qi asked me to order,

624
00:37:12,630 --> 00:37:13,940
and forgot the staple food.

625
00:37:13,940 --> 00:37:15,740
Go get some staple food quickly.

626
00:37:19,590 --> 00:37:21,190
Forgot to order staple food.

627
00:37:22,670 --> 00:37:24,350
Young people are careless.

628
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:26,150
Forgetting to order staple food

629
00:37:26,150 --> 00:37:27,150
is not a big deal.

630
00:37:27,670 --> 00:37:28,730
It's not a big deal,

631
00:37:30,400 --> 00:37:32,860
but it's the small things
that give you away.

632
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:36,170
Zhou Rong

633
00:37:36,590 --> 00:37:38,070
is very careful.

634
00:37:38,400 --> 00:37:39,230
But that doesn't mean

635
00:37:39,230 --> 00:37:40,280
everyone around him

636
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:41,210
will be careful.

637
00:37:42,110 --> 00:37:43,290
You mean

638
00:37:43,440 --> 00:37:45,070
to expand the surveillance range?

639
00:37:45,070 --> 00:37:45,480
Right.

640
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:47,770
You're right.

641
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:51,180
We need to find a chance to approach them.

642
00:37:51,880 --> 00:37:52,700
Hu Jianren is

643
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:54,030
Zhou Rong's trusted aide.

644
00:37:54,030 --> 00:37:54,560
Li Qian,

645
00:37:55,190 --> 00:37:56,310
starting tomorrow,

646
00:37:56,310 --> 00:37:57,910
you keep an eye on Hu Jianren.

647
00:37:58,320 --> 00:37:59,670
I'll keep an eye on Li Penggai.

648
00:37:59,670 --> 00:38:00,320
What did you say?

649
00:38:00,320 --> 00:38:02,580
He said he'll go keep an eye
on Li Penggai.

650
00:38:03,800 --> 00:38:05,550
Okay, you keep an eye on Li Penggai.

651
00:38:05,550 --> 00:38:06,320
Chief Qi, I suggest

652
00:38:06,320 --> 00:38:07,670
we split into more groups.

653
00:38:07,670 --> 00:38:09,330
Keep a close eye on all the key people

654
00:38:09,330 --> 00:38:10,330
around Zhou Rong.

655
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:11,600
If we can catch just one,

656
00:38:11,600 --> 00:38:13,000
we can track down the rest

657
00:38:13,320 --> 00:38:14,480
and make a breakthrough.

658
00:38:14,480 --> 00:38:14,960
Okay.

659
00:38:16,110 --> 00:38:17,040
Let's eat first.

660
00:38:21,550 --> 00:38:23,040
I'm finally back.

661
00:38:23,630 --> 00:38:24,190
Stop.

662
00:38:31,800 --> 00:38:32,860
Goodbye, brother.

663
00:38:33,260 --> 00:38:34,060
Driver, go on!

664
00:38:43,230 --> 00:38:43,760
Gai.

665
00:38:48,670 --> 00:38:50,280
You were supposed to hand in your computer

666
00:38:50,280 --> 00:38:52,000
when you left.

667
00:38:51,450 --> 00:38:53,650
[Du Cong, staff of Zhou Rong's company]

668
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:53,510
I didn't let them.

669
00:38:53,710 --> 00:38:54,760
I told them not to touch it,

670
00:38:54,760 --> 00:38:56,150
or else Gai would make life hard
for all of them

671
00:38:56,150 --> 00:38:57,150
when he came back.

672
00:38:57,630 --> 00:38:58,560
You're the best.

673
00:38:59,630 --> 00:39:00,360
The best bro.

674
00:39:04,190 --> 00:39:05,190
Is your promotion

675
00:39:05,880 --> 00:39:06,540
confirmed?

676
00:39:07,110 --> 00:39:08,110
Confirmed or not,

677
00:39:10,510 --> 00:39:12,710
I won't be staying here for long anyway.

678
00:39:13,230 --> 00:39:14,060
Gai,

679
00:39:14,440 --> 00:39:16,590
is the company's S600

680
00:39:17,190 --> 00:39:18,590
being used these days?

681
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:21,020
We have so many cars. Why use that one?

682
00:39:26,070 --> 00:39:27,800
Did Li ask to borrow a car again?

683
00:39:30,510 --> 00:39:31,320
Not again.

684
00:39:32,230 --> 00:39:33,490
This is the first time.

685
00:39:34,280 --> 00:39:35,320
I know, Gai.

686
00:39:35,360 --> 00:39:36,360
It's not the right time yet.

687
00:39:36,360 --> 00:39:37,020
Say no more.

688
00:39:37,630 --> 00:39:38,690
It's not easy for Li

689
00:39:38,920 --> 00:39:40,320
to run a wedding company.

690
00:39:41,230 --> 00:39:42,510
You two finally started dating.

691
00:39:42,510 --> 00:39:43,110
How can you not lend her a car

692
00:39:43,110 --> 00:39:43,760
when she asks?

693
00:39:43,760 --> 00:39:44,230
Lend it.

694
00:39:45,400 --> 00:39:46,800
Mr. Rong has so many cars.

695
00:39:46,800 --> 00:39:48,530
He won't mind one less. Lend it.

696
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:51,400
Gai.

697
00:39:51,480 --> 00:39:51,920
Hey, hey,

698
00:39:51,920 --> 00:39:52,510
what are you doing?

699
00:39:52,510 --> 00:39:53,570
What are you doing?

700
00:39:54,230 --> 00:39:54,760
Stand up.

701
00:39:55,760 --> 00:39:56,920
Look at you.

702
00:40:00,480 --> 00:40:00,940
Take it.

703
00:40:03,710 --> 00:40:04,740
Drive safely.

704
00:40:05,400 --> 00:40:06,380
Thanks, Gai.

705
00:40:12,660 --> 00:40:14,860
Give me two servings of meat dumplings.

706
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:15,830
And then?

707
00:40:16,150 --> 00:40:16,840
Eggs...

708
00:40:17,440 --> 00:40:18,630
Give me three eggs.

709
00:40:18,710 --> 00:40:19,840
Here, three for you.

710
00:40:20,550 --> 00:40:21,510
Need anything else?

711
00:40:21,510 --> 00:40:22,440
Get me some milk.

712
00:40:22,990 --> 00:40:24,030
I paid you.

713
00:40:30,000 --> 00:40:30,510
Thanks.

714
00:40:30,630 --> 00:40:31,280
A milk too.

715
00:40:31,360 --> 00:40:32,070
I don't drink that.

716
00:40:32,070 --> 00:40:33,000
Not that one. This one.

717
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:33,660
Sure thing.

718
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:34,600
Take care.

719
00:40:36,800 --> 00:40:37,960
What are you honking for?

720
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:38,800
No manners.

721
00:40:50,880 --> 00:40:52,360
Shy.

722
00:40:52,360 --> 00:40:53,360
S-H-Y.

723
00:40:57,670 --> 00:40:58,840
Hu Jianren didn't go to the company.

724
00:40:58,840 --> 00:40:59,440
I repeat,

725
00:40:59,510 --> 00:41:01,510
Hu Jianren didn't go to the company.

726
00:41:01,540 --> 00:41:12,020
[Sanjiangkou Children's Training Center]

727
00:41:32,150 --> 00:41:34,560
This is a little girl.

728
00:41:34,920 --> 00:41:38,090
-This is a little girl.
-This is a little girl.

729
00:41:38,230 --> 00:41:40,320
And she has a little curl.

730
00:41:40,670 --> 00:41:44,310
-And she has a little curl.
-And she has a little curl.

731
00:41:50,410 --> 00:41:53,240
-And when she is bad...
-And when she is bad...

732
00:41:53,320 --> 00:41:55,920
She is very, very bad.

733
00:41:56,000 --> 00:41:59,320
-She is...
-She is very, very bad.

734
00:41:59,410 --> 00:42:00,210
What's wrong?

735
00:42:00,880 --> 00:42:03,440
I want to go to WC.

736
00:42:03,510 --> 00:42:04,920
No, no, no, listen to me.

737
00:42:05,070 --> 00:42:07,070
I want to go to toilet.

738
00:42:08,060 --> 00:42:10,480
I want go to toilet.

739
00:42:10,670 --> 00:42:11,440
Toilet.

740
00:42:11,880 --> 00:42:12,280
Toi...

741
00:42:12,480 --> 00:42:14,090
Teacher, it's urgent.

742
00:42:14,210 --> 00:42:15,060
Go ahead.

743
00:42:15,440 --> 00:42:16,040
Thank you.

744
00:42:36,700 --> 00:42:38,270
This is the children's center.

745
00:42:38,270 --> 00:42:40,360
There are only kids taking classes inside.

746
00:42:40,360 --> 00:42:41,890
Who is he going to meet here?

747
00:42:43,510 --> 00:42:44,370
Keep watching.

748
00:42:44,880 --> 00:42:46,610
There must be something wrong.

749
00:42:48,760 --> 00:42:51,080
He is a bit shy.

750
00:42:51,320 --> 00:42:54,360
-He is a bit shy.
-He is a bit shy.

751
00:42:54,360 --> 00:42:54,880
Bit.

752
00:42:55,400 --> 00:42:56,280
Bit.

753
00:42:56,510 --> 00:42:57,030
Bit.

754
00:42:57,510 --> 00:42:58,320
Bit.

755
00:43:05,150 --> 00:43:05,630
Halt.
